00:12:44.461 --> 00:12:48.436
HUMANS REALLY ARE.

00:13:00.093 --> 00:13:01.328
&gt;&gt; Nia: HAIL FELLOW. WELL MET.

00:13:01.328 --> 00:13:02.765
I DO NOT UNDERSTAND.

00:13:02.765 --> 00:13:04.802
HOW ARE YOU THE SAME AS I AM?

00:13:04.802 --> 00:13:05.804
&gt;&gt; Simon: EH?

00:13:05.804 --> 00:13:07.207
&gt;&gt; Nia: YOU HAVE NO TAIL, NO

00:13:07.207 --> 00:13:08.910
CLAWS, NO FEATHERS.

00:13:08.910 --> 00:13:11.315
THAT AND YOUR SKIN IS SO SOFT.

00:13:11.315 --> 00:13:12.250
&gt;&gt; Simon: WELL, THAT’S ONLY

00:13:12.250 --> 00:13:12.985
NATURAL.

00:13:12.985 --> 00:13:13.553
I MEAN, AFTER ALL,

00:13:13.553 --> 00:13:14.856
I’M A HUMAN BEING.

00:13:14.856 --> 00:13:16.058
&gt;&gt; Nia: "HUMAN BEING"?

00:13:16.058 --> 00:13:17.828
&gt;&gt; Simon: YEAH. A HUMAN.

00:13:17.828 --> 00:13:20.901
YOU KNOW, LIKE A PERSON.

00:13:20.901 --> 00:13:22.070
&gt;&gt; Nia: PLEASE TELL ME,

00:13:22.070 --> 00:13:24.509
WHAT EXACTLY IS A HUMAN?

00:13:24.509 --> 00:13:25.878
HOW DO YOU DO, SIR.

00:13:25.878 --> 00:13:27.113
IT’S LOVELY TO MEET YOU.

00:13:27.113 --> 00:13:27.982
I’M NIA.

00:13:27.982 --> 00:13:32.892
NOW THEN, WHAT’S YOUR NAME?

00:13:32.892 --> 00:13:34.529
&gt;&gt; THERE’S NO ESCAPE,

00:13:34.529 --> 00:13:36.398
FILTHY HUMANS.

00:13:36.398 --> 00:13:40.273
&gt;&gt; Nia: I KNOW THAT VOICE.

00:13:40.273 --> 00:13:41.075
&gt;&gt; Yoko: ARE YOU STUPID

00:13:41.075 --> 00:13:45.049
OR SOMETHING?!

00:13:45.049 --> 00:13:45.951
&gt;&gt; Nia: STOP THIS AT ONCE,

00:13:45.951 --> 00:13:46.553
ADIANE!

00:13:46.553 --> 00:13:48.255
FIRST PRINCESS NIA, DAUGHTER

00:13:48.255 --> 00:13:50.393
OF SPIRAL KING LORDGENOME!

00:13:50.393 --> 00:13:51.428
I COMMAND YOU TO LEAVE,

00:13:51.428 --> 00:13:52.865
ADIANE, THE ELEGANT!

00:13:52.865 --> 00:13:59.378
ARE YOU NOT AWARE OF WHO I AM?

00:13:59.378 --> 00:14:01.315
&gt;&gt; YOU REALLY PISS ME OFF!

00:14:01.315 --> 00:14:02.317
IF YOU WANNA GO, TAKE YOUR OWN

00:14:02.317 --> 00:14:05.156
SORRY ASS!

00:14:05.156 --> 00:14:06.191
&gt;&gt; Nia: SO DOES THIS MEAN

00:14:06.191 --> 00:14:07.360
YOU HATE ME TOO, ADIANE?

00:14:07.360 --> 00:14:08.897
&gt;&gt; HATE YOU?

00:14:08.897 --> 00:14:09.599
I REALLY COULDN’T CARE LESS

00:14:09.599 --> 00:14:13.239
ABOUT YOU. [laughs]

00:14:13.239 --> 00:14:14.876
I WAS TOLD TO KILL YOU,

00:14:14.876 --> 00:14:16.245
SO THAT’S PRECISELY WHAT I’M

00:14:16.245 --> 00:14:17.447
GOING TO DO!

00:14:17.447 --> 00:14:18.416
&gt;&gt; Nia: IF MY FATHER ORDERED YOU

00:14:18.416 --> 00:14:19.852
TO TAKE YOUR OWN LIFE,

00:14:19.852 --> 00:14:21.523
WOULD YOU DO THAT TOO?

00:14:21.523 --> 00:14:22.625
YOU’VE GOT THIS ALL WRONG,

00:14:22.625 --> 00:14:23.960
ADIANE!

00:14:23.960 --> 00:14:25.296
THESE PEOPLE ARE DECENT AND

00:14:25.296 --> 00:14:26.398
GOOD, AND THEY HAVE DONE NOTHING

00:14:26.398 --> 00:14:27.434
WRONG!

00:14:27.434 --> 00:14:28.570
DON’T YOU THINK THERE MIGHT BE

00:14:28.570 --> 00:14:30.039
SOMETHING WRONG WITH THAT?

00:14:30.039 --> 00:14:31.008
&gt;&gt; NO, I DON’T, BECAUSE

00:14:31.008 --> 00:14:34.314
THERE ISN’T!

00:14:34.314 --> 00:14:38.924
&gt;&gt; Nia: LIKE A DOLL?

00:14:38.924 --> 00:14:40.627
&gt;&gt; Guame: NOW I’VE BEEN TOLD YOU

00:14:40.627 --> 00:14:42.097
ACTUALLY ASKED HIM STRAIGHT TO

00:14:42.097 --> 00:14:44.367
HIS FACE, "WHY WAS I BORN?"

00:14:44.367 --> 00:14:46.238
THAT WAS A BAD MOVE.

00:14:46.238 --> 00:14:47.541
HIS MAJESTY DETESTS HUMAN

00:14:47.541 --> 00:14:48.877
SELF‐AWARENESS.

00:14:48.877 --> 00:14:50.146
BUT WHO CAN BLAME HIM?

00:14:50.146 --> 00:14:51.448
WHY WOULD A PUPPET, A SIMPLE

00:14:51.448 --> 00:14:58.362
PLAYTHING, NEED SELF‐AWARENESS?

00:14:58.362 --> 00:15:00.366
&gt;&gt; Nia: SO I’M...I’M JUST LIKE

00:15:00.366 --> 00:15:03.038
THAT DOLL.

00:15:03.038 --> 00:15:04.374
&gt;&gt; YES, THAT’S RIGHT.

00:15:04.374 --> 00:15:05.410
AND SOMEDAY THEY’LL BE

00:15:05.410 --> 00:15:06.378
DISCARDED...

00:15:06.378 --> 00:15:12.892
EXACTLY LIKE YOU WERE!

00:15:12.892 --> 00:15:16.966
[laughing]

00:15:24.515 --> 00:15:26.084
&gt;&gt; Nia: YOU KNOW...

00:15:26.084 --> 00:15:28.222
YOU’LL NEVER BE YOUR BRO.

00:15:28.222 --> 00:15:29.391
I THINK YOU SHOULD ALWAYS BE

00:15:29.391 --> 00:15:30.426
YOURSELF.

00:15:30.426 --> 00:15:32.397
[giggles]

00:15:32.397 --> 00:15:33.600
&gt;&gt; Kamina: LISTEN, SIMON.

00:15:33.600 --> 00:15:35.169
NEVER FORGET THIS.

00:15:35.169 --> 00:15:36.639
BELIEVE IN YOURSELF.

00:15:36.639 --> 00:15:37.641
NOT IN THE SIMON THAT I HAVE

00:15:37.641 --> 00:15:39.111
FAITH IN.

00:15:39.111 --> 00:15:39.979
NOT IN THE KAMINA THAT YOU

00:15:39.979 --> 00:15:41.348
BELIEVE IN, EITHER.

00:15:41.348 --> 00:15:42.484
BELIEVE IN THE SIMON...

00:15:42.484 --> 00:15:45.423
&gt;&gt; Simon: WHO BELIEVES IN YOU!

00:15:45.423 --> 00:15:51.235
[gasps]

00:15:51.235 --> 00:15:52.270
&gt;&gt; Nia: SIMON WILL NEVER LOSE

00:15:52.270 --> 00:15:53.205
TO THE LIKES OF YOU!

00:15:53.205 --> 00:16:00.419
[gasps]

00:16:00.419 --> 00:16:01.556
&gt;&gt; Simon: NIA, I’M HERE TO

00:16:01.556 --> 00:16:02.423
RESCUE YOU!

00:16:02.423 --> 00:16:06.966
COME ON!

00:16:06.966 --> 00:16:11.509
&gt;&gt; Nia: SIMON!

00:16:11.509 --> 00:16:13.379
&gt;&gt; Simon: AND NOW I UNDERSTAND!

00:16:13.379 --> 00:16:14.549
&gt;&gt; Nia: SO DO I.

00:16:14.549 --> 00:16:17.187
THANKS A LOT, SIMON!

00:16:17.187 --> 00:16:18.523
&gt;&gt; Simon: MY BRO IS DEAD.

00:16:18.523 --> 00:16:20.359
HE’S GONE.

00:16:20.359 --> 00:16:22.497
BUT HE’S RIGHT THERE ON MY BACK

00:16:22.497 --> 00:16:23.733
AND HERE IN MY HEART!

00:16:23.733 --> 00:16:28.977
HE LIVES ON AS PART OF ME!

00:16:28.977 --> 00:16:29.712
IF YOU’RE GONNA DIG,

00:16:29.712 --> 00:16:31.481
DIG TO THE HEAVENS.

00:16:31.481 --> 00:16:32.551
NO MATTER WHAT’S IN MY WAY,

00:16:32.551 --> 00:16:33.620
I WON’T STOP.

00:16:33.620 --> 00:16:35.022
ONCE I’VE DUG THROUGH,

00:16:35.022 --> 00:16:36.526
IT MEANS THAT I’VE WON!

00:16:36.526 --> 00:16:37.528
&gt;&gt; YOU WHAT?

00:16:37.528 --> 00:16:39.532
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

00:16:39.532 --> 00:16:40.333
&gt;&gt; Simon: JUST WHO THE HELL DO

00:16:40.333 --> 00:16:41.703
YOU THINK I AM?

00:16:41.703 --> 00:16:43.472
I’M SIMON.

00:16:43.472 --> 00:16:45.376
I’M NOT MY BRO.

00:16:45.376 --> 00:16:46.746
I’M ME...

00:16:46.746 --> 00:16:51.488
SIMON THE DIGGER!

00:16:51.488 --> 00:16:56.231
FINISHING MOVE.

00:16:56.231 --> 00:16:56.766
&gt;&gt; NO WAY.

00:16:56.766 --> 00:17:00.239
&gt;&gt; Yoko: THAT MOVE WAS A...

00:17:09.124 --> 00:17:11.194
&gt;&gt; Simon: GIGA...

00:17:11.194 --> 00:17:13.499
DRILL...

00:17:13.499 --> 00:17:16.606
BREAK!

00:17:31.636 --> 00:17:32.504
PUT HER DOWN!

00:17:32.504 --> 00:17:37.146
LET NIA GO!

00:17:37.146 --> 00:17:37.648
[screams]

00:17:37.648 --> 00:17:41.723
&gt;&gt; GENERAL ADIANE!

00:17:41.723 --> 00:17:44.662
&gt;&gt; Simon: NO, YOU DON’T!

00:18:06.673 --> 00:18:08.643
&gt;&gt; DAMN YOU.

00:18:08.643 --> 00:18:11.582
DAMN YOU, GURREN LAGANN!

00:18:11.582 --> 00:18:12.751
DAMN!

00:18:17.160 --> 00:18:19.732
&gt;&gt; THE TIME HAS FINALLY COME

00:18:19.732 --> 00:18:22.738
TO DEMONSTRATE MY POWER.

00:18:22.738 --> 00:18:25.076
YOUR MAJESTY, THE SPIRAL KING,

00:18:25.076 --> 00:18:28.617
WATCH THIS BATTLE CLOSELY!

00:18:28.617 --> 00:18:32.390
ALL UNITS, ADVANCE!

