&gt;&gt; Lordgenome: WHAT ARE HUMANS?

00:19:12.203 --> 00:19:14.207
WELL, DO YOU REALLY WISH

00:19:14.207 --> 00:19:16.679
TO KNOW THE ANSWER?

00:19:16.679 --> 00:19:19.552
DO YOU, VIRAL?

00:19:19.552 --> 00:19:21.823
&gt;&gt; YES!

00:19:26.699 --> 00:19:28.302
&gt;&gt; Simon: BRO, I COULD NEVER BE

00:19:28.302 --> 00:19:30.807
YOU, BUT I’M GOING OFF TO DO

00:19:30.807 --> 00:19:33.245
