00:19:33.245 --> 00:19:37.588
[Boota grunts]

00:19:37.588 --> 00:19:38.857
THE THINGS THAT ONLY SIMON

00:19:38.857 --> 00:19:42.497
THE DIGGER CAN DO.

00:19:53.285 --> 00:19:57.561
[yelling]

00:20:17.735 --> 00:20:20.674
[screaming]

00:20:25.650 --> 00:20:26.919
&gt;&gt; Lordgenome: WHAT’S WRONG?

00:20:26.919 --> 00:20:28.489
HAS ALL YOUR SPIRAL POWER

00:20:28.489 --> 00:20:30.259
