00:20:35.002 --> 00:20:36.706
THEN I’LL BELIEVE IN YOU WITH

00:20:36.706 --> 00:20:38.275
EVERY FIBER OF MY BEING!

00:20:38.275 --> 00:20:41.916
SO PLEASE, PLEASE WIN!

00:20:41.916 --> 00:20:48.328
[laughing]

00:20:48.328 --> 00:20:49.464
&gt;&gt; Lordgenome: I HAVEN’T HAD

00:20:49.464 --> 00:20:51.636
THIS MUCH FUN IN A LONG TIME,

00:20:51.636 --> 00:20:52.871
BOY.

00:20:52.871 --> 00:20:54.742
NOW, BACK INTO THE DIRT

00:20:54.742 --> 00:20:59.752
WITH YOU!

00:20:59.752 --> 00:21:01.789
A CORE DRILL?!

00:21:01.789 --> 00:21:03.760
&gt;&gt; Simon: AND THAT SOMETHING IS

00:21:03.760 --> 00:21:06.999
MY DRILL!

00:21:15.951 --> 00:21:17.320
&gt;&gt; Lordgenome: I SEE.

00:21:17.320 --> 00:21:18.990
YOUR SPIRAL POWER HAS GROWN

00:21:18.990 --> 00:21:22.664
SUFFICIENT TO OUTSTRIP MY OWN.

00:21:22.664 --> 00:21:24.535
&gt;&gt; Simon: LORDGENOME.

00:21:24.535 --> 00:21:25.436
